data.text: @LOPprimetime @dennmart Though Heenan's claim that he purposefully paired the celebrities with the least interview-able people was hilarious.

@LOPprimetime @dennmart I mean, I expect weird celebrities. I expect mildly racist jokes. But I DON'T expect one of the biggest stars to show up for a throwaway tag match, and I don't expect the other two things to converge on that moment!
@SpectralGent @dennmart It happens so often in those days I think it has to come from Vince.
